  <brief_title>Assessment of Cardiac Fixation During PET Using a New Drug Within Amyloid Cardiac Injuries.</brief_title>
  <acronym>AMYLCAR</acronym>
  <official_title>Assessment of Cardiac Fixation During Positron Emission Tomography (PET) Examination Using 18F-Flutemetamol (Vizamyl ®) Within Amyloid Cardiac Injuries.</official_title>
